OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe inquest into the death of Noah
OL,8,FDonohoe has heard police dedicated a
OL,9,F"significant amount of officers" to
OL,10,Fsearch for the schoolboy in the days
OL,11,Fafter he went missing.
OL,13,FA police witness told Belfast
OL,14,FCoroner's Court that he believed the
OL,15,Fhigh risk level of the case was
OL,16,Frecognised quickly.
OL,18,FThe inquest into the death of the 14-
OL,19,Fyear-old which is being heard with a
OL,20,Fjury, has now entered its ninth week.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
