OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FNoah's naked body was found in a storm
OL,8,Fdrain tunnel in north Belfast in June
OL,9,F2020, six days after he left home on
OL,10,Fhis bike to meet two friends in the
OL,11,FCavehill area of the city.
OL,13,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,14,Fcause of death was likely to be
OL,15,Fdrowning.
OL,17,FThe inquest resumed on Monday morning
OL,18,Fwith evidence from Inspector Bell, who
OL,19,Fwas a sergeant in June 2020 and had
OL,20,Fbeen involved in the investigation to
OL,21,Ffind Noah.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FInspector Bell told the inquest he had
OL,8,Fbeen carrying out inquiries in
OL,9,FNorthwood Road on Tuesday June 23, two
OL,10,Fdays after Noah had gone missing.
OL,12,FHe said he had observed CCTV footage
OL,13,Fon a mobile phone of a youth cycling
OL,14,Fnaked in the area.
OL,16,FThe officer told the jury that the
OL,17,Fprevious day, he was the morning duty
OL,18,Fsergeant in Lisburn Road police
OL,19,Fstation when he was told by an
OL,20,Finspector he would be co-ordinating
OL,21,Fthe investigation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said: "On the Monday there were a
OL,8,Flot of actions that needed to be
OL,9,Fdelegated and co-ordinated and
OL,10,Fdifferent updates coming in.
OL,12,F"When I come on duty I want to be
OL,13,Ffully aware of the investigation."
OL,15,FCounsel to the coroner, Peter Coll,
OL,16,Fasked the witness if there was a
OL,17,F"checklist" of things he was checking.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUuD@bO]yD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe officer said he worked off a
OL,8,Ftemplate but added extra actions
OL,9,F"tailored to the individual
OL,10,Finvestigation".
OL,12,FHe said there were two sergeants on
OL,13,Fduty on the Monday. He said one looked
OL,14,Fafter other duties while he
OL,15,Fconcentrated on the Noah search
OL,16,Fbecause "we both recognised the
OL,17,Fsignificant risk".
OL,19,FHe added: "We certainly did allocate a
OL,20,Fsignificant amount of officers to this
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@NO]xD@IOUyD@QO]{D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"When you look at the timeline of my
OL,8,Femails and my phone calls, you can see
OL,9,Fthis investigation had me dedicated to
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,F"The risk, I believe, was recognised
OL,13,Fvery quickly."
OL,15,FHe said police dealt with missing
OL,16,Fperson investigations on the majority
OL,17,Fof days.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@DO]tD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FInspector Bell said the Cavehill area
OL,8,Fhad been checked overnight by air
OL,9,Fsupport and there was "no new
OL,10,Finformation" that further searches
OL,11,Fwere required.
OL,13,FHe said: "We had no information to say
OL,14,Fthat Noah was definitely in Cavehill,
OL,15,Fit was one of our hypothesis.
OL,17,F"He had plans to go there, however,
OL,18,Fthose plans were cancelled."
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@LO]uD@JOUyD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Coll asked the witness about how
OL,8,Fthe search progressed on the Monday,
OL,9,Fincluding the police's use of CCTV and
OL,10,FTLU (telecoms liaison unit) evidence.
OL,12,FThe officer said: "I think it is
OL,13,Fimportant to mention this was in the
OL,14,Fmiddle of Covid, so there wasn't a lot
OL,15,Fof people moving about.
OL,17,F"All of the officers were aware of
OL,18,FNoah's picture, that he was on a bike.
OL,19,FWe also had city centre CCTV operators
OL,20,Flooking for him as well."
OL,26,@tD@SOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe added: "We have to prioritise
OL,8,Fpolice resources to where we are most
OL,9,Flikely to get results, that could be
OL,10,Ffriends or family, he might be at a
OL,11,Ffriend's house, a family member's
OL,12,Fhouse, we were checking those
OL,13,Faddresses.
OL,15,F"One hypothesis was he had just woken
OL,16,Fup, he might have slept rough
OL,17,Fsomewhere."
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774275077
OL,3,CPolice 'recognised risk quickly' after
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe disappearance, inquest
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Bell said: "This is probably the
OL,8,Fdensest area of the country we are
OL,9,Flooking at where he could have gone
OL,10,Fany direction.
OL,12,F"Cavehill was one possible direction
OL,13,Fbut he could have gone anywhere."
OL,15,FThe inquest continues.
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
